// src/components/Footer.js
import React from "react";
import {
  Box,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  TextField,
  Button,
  IconButton,
} from "@mui/material";
import FacebookIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Facebook";
import InstagramIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Instagram";
import TwitterIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Twitter";
import PinterestIcon from "@mui/icons-material/Pinterest";

export default function Footer() {
  return (
    <Box
      sx={{
        mt: 8,
        p: 6,
        background: "linear-gradient(180deg, #ffe0eb, #ffd6df)",
        color: "#7a3550",
        fontFamily: "'Quicksand', sans-serif",
      }}
    >
      <Grid container spacing={4}>
        {/* About Section */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mb: 2, fontFamily: "'Sacramento', cursive", fontSize: "1.8rem" }}>
            SweetCraft
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2">
            Handcrafted desserts made with love! Customize your waffles, pancakes, pastries, cookies, bento cakes & more.
          </Typography>
        </Grid>

        {/* Quick Links */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
            Quick Links
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ cursor: "pointer", "&:hover": { color: "#ff4f7b" } }}>Home</Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ cursor: "pointer", "&:hover": { color: "#ff4f7b" } }}>Categories</Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ cursor: "pointer", "&:hover": { color: "#ff4f7b" } }}>My Orders</Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ cursor: "pointer", "&:hover": { color: "#ff4f7b" } }}>Contact</Typography>
        </Grid>

        {/* Newsletter */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
            Newsletter
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
            Subscribe for updates, special offers & sweet surprises!
          </Typography>
          <Box display="flex" gap={1}>
            <TextField
              placeholder="Your email"
              size="small"
              sx={{ backgroundColor: "#fff", borderRadius: 1, flex: 1 }}
            />
            <Button
              variant="contained"
              sx={{
                background: "linear-gradient(45deg, #ff9ebc, #ff6f91)",
                "&:hover": { background: "linear-gradient(45deg, #ff6388ff, #ff9ebc)" },
              }}
            >
              Subscribe
            </Button>
          </Box>
        </Grid>

        {/* Social / Contact */}
        <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
          <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
            Connect With Us
          </Typography>
          <Box display="flex" gap={1}>
            <IconButton sx={{ color: "#ff4f7b" }}><FacebookIcon /></IconButton>
            <IconButton sx={{ color: "#ff4f7b" }}><InstagramIcon /></IconButton>
            <IconButton sx={{ color: "#ff4f7b" }}><TwitterIcon /></IconButton>
            <IconButton sx={{ color: "#ff4f7b" }}><PinterestIcon /></IconButton>
          </Box>
          <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ mt: 2 }}>
            Email: support@sweetcraft.com
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body2">
            Phone: +91 98765 43210
          </Typography>
        </Grid>
      </Grid>

      <Box sx={{ textAlign: "center", mt: 4, borderTop: "1px solid #ffb6c1", pt: 2 }}>
        <Typography variant="body2" sx={{ color: "#7a3550" }}>
          Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} SweetCraft. All rights reserved.
        </Typography>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
